@startuml
title Sueca - Fluxo Atual Lobby/Waiting (GraphQL + WebSocket)

actor "Jogador" as User
participant "Flutter UI" as UI
participant "GraphqlService" as GQLClient
participant "GraphQL API" as GQL
participant "LobbyRepository" as LobbyRepo
participant "WebSocketService" as WSF
participant "Hub/RoomHub" as Hub
participant "RoomWaitingController" as WaitCtrl

== 1) Login/Register ==
User -> UI : autenticar
UI -> GQLClient : mutation login/register
GQLClient -> GQL : request
GQL --> GQLClient : user{id,username}
GQLClient --> UI : sessao iniciada

== 2) Lobby list ==
UI -> LobbyRepo : fetchRooms()
LobbyRepo -> GQLClient : query rooms
GQLClient -> GQL : request
GQL --> GQLClient : rooms[]
GQLClient --> UI : lista de salas

note right of UI
A lista de salas e carregada por query GraphQL.
Nao ha stream realtime continuo no lobby principal.
end note

== 3) Criar/Entrar sala ==
alt criar sala
  UI -> GQLClient : mutation createRoom(hostId)
  GQLClient -> GQL : request
  GQL --> GQLClient : room{id,status,players}
else entrar sala
  UI -> GQLClient : mutation joinRoom(roomId,userId)
  GQLClient -> GQL : request
  GQL --> GQLClient : room atualizada
end

== 4) Waiting room websocket ==
UI -> WSF : connect(roomId, playerId)
WSF -> Hub : /ws?roomId&playerId
Hub --> WSF : socket ativo

UI -> WaitCtrl : initialize()
WaitCtrl -> GQLClient : query room(id)
GQLClient -> GQL : request
GQL --> GQLClient : room details
GQLClient --> WaitCtrl : RoomDetails

loop quando chega evento WS da sala
  Hub --> WSF : event JSON
  WSF --> WaitCtrl : LobbyRealtimeEvent
  WaitCtrl -> GQLClient : query room(id)
  GQLClient -> GQL : request
  GQL --> GQLClient : room atualizado
  GQLClient --> WaitCtrl : refresh estado local
end

== 5) Acoes na waiting room ==
alt mudar bot strategy
  UI -> WSF : send(change_bot_strategy, option)
else iniciar jogo
  UI -> GQLClient : mutation startGame(roomId)
  GQLClient -> GQL : request
  GQL --> GQLClient : room status=IN_GAME
  UI -> UI : navegar para GamePage
end

@enduml
